      "description": "Hi there! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner! This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single blemish; it\u2019s just that perfect! If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel and a ride that\u2019s been loved with all my heart, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
