    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black, representing a benchmark in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression and a recently overhauled VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and fresh rod bearings. The suspension geometry remains true, with all bushings and dampers providing the communicative, razor-sharp handling characteristics synonymous with the chassis. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance and an immaculate undercarriage.",
      "price": 46500.0,
